Megatron notted Domnijoe's loyalty. Another robot to surround himself
by, he notted. He knew that if Motormaster was here, he would follow
him, but a lot of these robots he hasnt known for a while. Ironic, how
before he was thinking about taking Firestrike under his wing, and
primping him for Leadership. How funny it is, that that changed with but
a challenge from the hot headed robot.
